Class ElementStore<E>

Type Parameters:
E -
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Iterable<E>, Collection<E>
public class ElementStore<E>
extends CollectionAbstract<E>

An ElementStore is a simple Collection for any elements which ensures simple persistence to any provided ElementStore.PersistenceAccessor.

The Collection can only contain one instance out of two equal ones. To detect equality it uses the Object.equals(Object) method. This behavior is similar to a HashSet.

Author:
Omnaest
